      "id": "attack-pattern--468da90b-0c26-4d4d-9ec3-dc2f966135ec",
      "name": "Persistence via Boot Receiver and Foreground Service",
      "description": "Frogblight maintains persistence on infected devices through a broadcast receiver that triggers on boot completion and a foreground service that interacts with the C2.",
